# SariSari Snaps — marketing site env (Vite). Copy to .env.local and fill in.
# Same Apps Script Web App the configurator uses (it already has Mailchimp wired
# up). This site only ever sends action: "subscribeEmail" — it never touches
# Drive, the Orders Sheet, or anything order-related.

VITE_APPS_SCRIPT_URL=
VITE_API_TOKEN=
